title: ROGUE OF THE RANGE ｜ Johnny Mack Brow

sources.title: ROGUE OF THE RANGE ｜ Johnny Mack Brow
sources.description: Rogue of the Range is a 1936 American Western film directed by S. Roy Luby and starring Johnny Mack Brown, Lois January and in her only film, Phyllis Hume, Miss California 1936 and first runner-up for Miss America, where she used the name Phyllis Dobson.
